{"tid":1579472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"披露示威者資料　起底網站獲央視認證　有受害人質疑公安爆料","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:39:36.000Z","uid":68738,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"17a771f0b4db5c52c9e52dccb02d557adc078b50","tid":1579472,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cctv-18_hWLa9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcctv-18_hWLa9_1200x0.png&h=1673148a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日網上出現一個「起底」網站，披露大量民主派人士、抗爭者及新聞工作者的個人資料，如今網站更獲大陸官媒認證。央視今日在微博發布一段影片，詳細顯示網站的網址及起底內容，又呼籲網民「認清這些嘴臉」。另有區議員引述被起底人士稱，曾經向大陸公安提供假地址，結果假地址亦在網站上出現，質疑是公安洩露港人資料。<br />\n<br />\n該「起底」網站近月在網上流傳，並提供了電郵地址呼籲網民爆料。網站內有民主派人士、立法會議員、學運成員的相片、電話、Facebook及地址。《蘋果日報》及《立場新聞》的記者資料亦被披露。<br />\n<br />\n央視今日在其官方微博發布一段聲稱是「網友製作」的影片，顯示了網站網址及起底資料。央視又呼籲網民轉發：「認清這些嘴臉！被摘下面罩香港暴徒名單&hellip;&hellip;摘下他們的面罩，一起行動！轉！」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外民主派沙田區區議員趙柱幫今日在 FB 發文，引述有被網站起底的「手足」稱，該人兩個月前於大陸過關時曾被公安扣留 5 小時，期間公安沒收手機檢查並發現事主參與遊行。公安之後要求他填寫口供紙，他刻意填寫了錯誤的地址，結果這錯誤地址亦在起底網站上出現，因此認為是公安洩露香港人的個人資料。</span><br />\n<br />\n個人資料私隱專員黃繼兒今日表示，由於涉事網站域名於俄羅斯登記，伺服器亦非設於香港，私隱專員公署無權要求域外機構提供網站營運者資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89-%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E7%88%86%E6%96%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599%2F&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=22ae8fb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599%2F&h=98963602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89-%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E7%88%86%E6%96%99/</a>"},{"pid":"0c92b37a1d47bc8b171bf1e0626ff1f0cc2d4f04","tid":1579472,"uid":18948,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"私隱專員公署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收一收皮啦"},{"pid":"2841e6b0da44d7cfacc2db8777b2e8ff84f7129b","tid":1579472,"uid":81273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"過關收人地資料就係搞呢d野恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6999edd3c1f516042e1e22011c2a2092eb382954","tid":1579472,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48848303cebc9e57928da2b825a7d3db1e77900b","tid":1579472,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推下呢個post，p牌仔推唔郁<br />\n<br />\n讓「Pokemon go」變成「榮光go」「文宣go」<b